  <brief_title>Incidence and Severity of Postoperative Sore Throat And Intubation Response by Using Different Devices for Endotracheal Intubation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Incidence and Severity of Postoperative Sore Throat And Intubation Response by Using Different Devices for Endotracheal Intubation</official_title>
